data.description: Tucked away in the serene Caldwood Forest, you'll find this one-story residence located at 4455 Sunbury in Beaumont, TX. Offering three bedrooms and two baths, this home holds immense potential and eagerly awaits your creative vision to transform it into a superb residence or investment opportunity. Inside, you'll be greeted by a warm wood-burning fireplace and an open floor plan that seamlessly connects the kitchen, dining, and living areas, providing space for all your daily activities. Stepping outside, you'll discover a generously sized backyard, perfect for outdoor enjoyment. Notable recent updates include a new roof installed in August 2023 and the replacement of the kitchen window facing the street. Convenience is a hallmark of this property, as it is conveniently located near shopping centers, dining options, and educational institutions. The seller has confirmed that the property has no history of flooding, providing peace of mind for potential buyers.
